data.text: @ronthecupid @bigchethan Glad to be of help. Do check out Doddakannelli and Halanayakanahalli PHCs. They seem to have open slots for 45+.
@sriharikraman @bigchethan Thank you for this help. i called Doctor Raghunath and he confirmed there is no stock for tomorrow at Kodathi PHC.

@ronthecupid @bigchethan I couldn't find any number on the outside of the PHC. Didn't want to enter. But I had taken the number of the medical officer here last time I had gotten my parents vaccinated. May be you can call them.

DR RAGHUNATH B B
MEDICAL OFFICER

CONTACT NO: 9845106993
@sriharikraman @bigchethan Thank you very much. They are still allowing appointments on CoWin. But If they do not have stock, it will save my parents the hassle of travel during lockdown.
@ronthecupid @bigchethan Let me check and get back to you. I have noticed that they have completely stopped vaccinated since 1st. But I'll check for the number and let you know.
@sriharikraman @bigchethan Is there any contact number of Kodathi PHC to confirm availability of stock? Any help is much appreciated.
@bigchethan The PHC right outside out apartment. Kodathi PHC.
@sriharikraman Lucky man. Where did u get it ?
